</math></stem> with stability at the <stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>12</mn></mrow></mrow></msup></math></stem> level and using a coin-sized laser module, <em>Optics Express</em>, <strong>23</strong>, 20749 (2015).</formattedref>
